      "description": "$31,900 - Clean, well-kept car in good condition that runs and drives very nicely. It presents well overall and would make a strong choice for someone wanting a dependable, attractive vehicle without paying top-of-market money. It shows normal cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but nothing that takes away from it being a solid, honest example.",
