      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition vehicle that runs and drives, but it shows clear signs of age and use throughout. Expect visible cosmetic wear on the exterior, some interior wear, and the kind of minor issues or deferred maintenance that are common on an older, well-used car. It can still be a workable driver for someone looking for a budget-friendly option, but buyers should come expecting imperfections rather than a fully restored or like-new example.",
      "price": 19800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a handy buyer, commuter backup, or project opportunity. It shows its age and will need attention, but it offers an affordable entry point for someone looking for dependable transportation potential without a big upfront cost. Priced to sell and represented honestly.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s a great fit for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone who doesn\u2019t mind a little cosmetic wear in exchange for real value. Priced to sell and represented honestly by a seller who believes in straightforward deals.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid candidate for someone who wants a usable project with good bones. This car presents as a driver-grade example with honest wear, but it still offers a strong mechanical feel and the kind of straightforward platform enthusiasts appreciate. The engine pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the sort of analog road manners that make it worth saving rather than parting out. Cosmetically it will need attention, and it\u2019s best approached as a budget-friendly restoration, weekend tinkering car, or dependable spare with character. If you know how to turn a wrench, there\u2019s real upside here.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Honest wear, priced right, ready to go. Great budget buy at $7,900.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its panels and plenty of life left for the right driver. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone seeking an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on project, or a dependable backup with personality. The cabin and body show their age, but that only adds to its no-nonsense charm: what you see is a car that\u2019s been lived in, driven, and ready for its next chapter. If you appreciate value, grit, and the chance to make something your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone looking for affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward value over perfection, but it still offers a chance to get behind the wheel at a very accessible price point. An honest, attractively priced option for the right buyer.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    }
